    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Polysilicone-30 is a complex crosslinked siloxane that is composed of both silsesquioxane and linear siloxane segments. It is formed by condensing Hydrolyzed Silk PG-Propyl Methylsilanediol with C6-10 alkyltriethoxy silane and dimethyldiethoxy silane and capping the resulting siloxane with trimethylchlorosilane."
